[gd_scene load_steps=27 format=3 uid="uid://b3degg0coopkhazad"]

; CO-OP KHAZAD-DUM (M19-style co-op set-piece, cloned from CoopPhalanx/CoopStand).
; Two captains (P1 keyboard+mouse, P2 gamepad) hold the great pillared hall of
; Dwarrowdelm against a horde of Moria goblins and the restless dead. Shared
; FollowCamera frames BOTH captains (Target + Target2 + DynamicZoom). Win = clear
; the horde; lose only when BOTH captains fall (GameManager RequireAllPlayersDead).
; Built entirely from NEW assets (dark Moria sky kit) + existing prefabs, so every
; other mode stays byte-identical.

